.TH CWE-89 7 "2026-06-15" "CWE Top 25 (2025)" "Software Weakness Reference"
.SH NAME
CWE\-89 \- Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command (SQL Injection)
.SH RANK
2025 CWE Top 25 rank: \fB#2\fR (2024 rank: 3).
.SH CLASSIFICATION
Class: Injection.
.SH DESCRIPTION
User input is concatenated into an SQL statement, so attacker\-supplied metacharacters change the query's meaning. This allows reading or modifying arbitrary data, authentication bypass, and sometimes command execution on the database host.
.SH MITIGATION
Use parameterized queries / prepared statements so the driver sends SQL structure and values separately. Apply least\-privilege DB accounts and allow\-list any identifier (table/column) that cannot be parameterized.
.SH KNOWN EXPLOITED VULNERABILITIES
CISA KEV catalog (as of 2026-06-15): \fB28\fR exploited CVEs mapped to this weakness.
.PP
CVE\-2016\-2386, CVE\-2017\-18362, CVE\-2018\-7841, CVE\-2019\-7481, CVE\-2019\-12989, CVE\-2020\-5722, CVE\-2020\-12271, CVE\-2020\-17463, CVE\-2020\-29574, CVE\-2021\-20016, CVE\-2021\-20028, CVE\-2021\-27101, CVE\-2021\-42258, CVE\-2021\-44026, CVE\-2023\-34362, CVE\-2023\-46748, CVE\-2023\-48788, CVE\-2024\-6670, CVE\-2024\-9379, CVE\-2024\-9465, CVE\-2024\-29824, CVE\-2024\-43468, CVE\-2025\-25181, CVE\-2025\-25257, CVE\-2025\-57819, CVE\-2026\-9082, CVE\-2026\-21643, CVE\-2026\-42208.
.SH EXAMPLES
One vulnerable\->fixed pair per ecosystem (Node.js, Python, Java, Go, PHP).
.SS Node.js
\fIVulnerable:\fR
.RS
.EX
// node-postgres
const r = await db.query(
  "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = '" + name + "'");   // injectable
.EE
.RE
\fIFixed:\fR
.RS
.EX
const r = await db.query(
  "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = $1", [name]);       // bound parameter
.EE
.RE
.SS Python
\fIVulnerable:\fR
.RS
.EX
q = "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = '%s'" % username   # injectable
conn.execute(q).fetchall()
.EE
.RE
\fIFixed:\fR
.RS
.EX
q = "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = ?"                  # placeholder
conn.execute(q, (username,)).fetchall()
.EE
.RE
.SS Java
\fIVulnerable:\fR
.RS
.EX
Statement st = conn.createStatement();
ResultSet rs = st.executeQuery(
  "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = '" + name + "'");    // injectable
.EE
.RE
\fIFixed:\fR
.RS
.EX
PreparedStatement ps = conn.prepareStatement(
  "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = ?");
ps.setString(1, name);                                   // bound parameter
ResultSet rs = ps.executeQuery();
.EE
.RE
.SS Go
\fIVulnerable:\fR
.RS
.EX
rows, _ := db.Query(
  "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = '" + name + "'")     // injectable
.EE
.RE
\fIFixed:\fR
.RS
.EX
rows, _ := db.Query(
  "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = ?", name)            // bound parameter
.EE
.RE
.SS PHP
\fIVulnerable:\fR
.RS
.EX
// PDO
$rows = $db->query(
  "SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = '" . $name . "'");   // injectable
.EE
.RE
\fIFixed:\fR
.RS
.EX
$stmt = $db->prepare("SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = ?");
$stmt->execute([$name]);                                 // bound parameter
$rows = $stmt->fetchAll();
.EE
.RE
